Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper is about object tracking using deep learning techniques.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of recurrent regression networks for tracking.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper involves developing a model that can adapt to new observations and modify its underlying model.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as object tracking is an important task in robotics applications.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper involves tracking objects in video sequences.
